Suicune (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0244: Entei
Pokémon
#0246: Larvitar →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Suicune (TCG Pocket).

Suicune has been featured on 24 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Revelation expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Suicune cards are normally Water-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Suicune

Suicune
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
